<h2 style="text-align: center">BIOTECHNOLOGY</h2>

<p>BiotechnologyÂ (or biotech) is the use of living systems and organisms to develop or make useful products, or "any technological application that uses biological systems, living organisms or derivatives thereof, to make or modify products or processes for specific use".
<p style="text-align: right">(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biotechnology)

<p><b>Potential / Applications of Biotechnology: -</b> 

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#8226 Medicine
